{"tid":767842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"風流倜儻撩交打 梁朝偉靠靚仔攻陷歐洲","createTime":"2018-08-05T01:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T15:39:28.000Z","uid":82917,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a12decf90b6753a488778f678fed5ed087361487","tid":767842,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:49:29.000Z","msg":"由馬楚成執導、梁朝偉、<del>吳亦凡、唐嫣、杜鵑</del>等主演的新片之製作特輯曝光，短短兩分鐘內，幾位主角無懼危險親自上陣，花式迴旋踢、360空翻、飛簷走壁，一拳一腳都都充滿狠勁！為呈現歐陸風情，拍攝前，馬導演專程飛往歐洲七次作實地考察，細心研究各國地標建築、了解當地風土民情。拍攝期間，攝製隊來到各大城市取景，當中包括米蘭火車站、羅馬古建築、巴里海灘等，歐洲風光一覽無遺！ <br />\n<br />\n在電影特輯中，梁朝偉在天台的動作畫面亦令人印象深刻，前一秒玩緊花式空翻，下一秒帥氣旋轉，「吸睛」！不過，看起來酷爆的一幕，拍攝時卻充滿驚險，梁朝偉也忍不住說：「一不小心就會掉下去！」令人替他抹了一把汗。而吳亦凡也在電影中過足了打戲癮，更巧用彈力球，機智帥氣！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/094827_a95622e2276ce121ef4561f3cbe6ff16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F094827_a95622e2276ce121ef4561f3cbe6ff16.png&h=80f5b805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌那星！就黎六張都咁撚靚仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/094809_44e40c30bb851c1971b43769087be946.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F094809_44e40c30bb851c1971b43769087be946.png&h=6c81e293&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/094810_533e78bf972aebb8ac8ca30ea5dbbfb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F094810_533e78bf972aebb8ac8ca30ea5dbbfb6.png&h=e975e596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<im